@startuml duanfuxiang0_MysqlMigrationTool
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

database "Source MySQL" as SourceDB
component "Binlog Parser" as Parser
component "Row Event Handler" as Handler
component "Data Mapper" as Mapper
database "Target Database" as TargetDB

SourceDB --> Parser : Binlog Events
Parser --> Handler : Parsed Events
Handler --> Mapper : Row Data
Mapper --> TargetDB : SQL Operations

note right of Parser
  Uses go-mysql/canal
  to capture and parse
  binlog events
end note

note right of Handler
  Implements canal.EventHandler
  Processes inserts/updates/deletes
end note

note right of Mapper
  Uses reflection to map
  binlog data to Go structs
  (User, Email, Mobile)
end note

note right of TargetDB
  Applies changes via
  InsertToNew/UpdateToNew/
  DeleteFromNew methods
end note
@enduml